      "qualityofcareadults_emergencyroom_wait_paintreated_past12months_opt_4": "More than 1 hour but less than 2 hours",
      "qualityofcareadults_emergencyroom_wait_paintreated_past12months_opt_5": "2 hours or more",
      "qualityofcareadults_ratingcare_received_past12months": "Using any number from 0 to 10 where 0 is the worst care possible and 10 is the best care possible, what number would you use to rate all of the care you received for your health in the last 12 months?",
